data.description: Back on the market!!  Discover the epitome of modern comfort at 1306 Creekland Ct, where this beautifully remodeled home awaits. Boasting three spacious bedrooms and the potential for a fourth, this residence has been completely renovated to offer a contemporary haven.  Step inside to be greeted by luxurious LVP flooring that graces the majority of the home, providing durability and a touch of elegance. New carpet on steps and upper bedrooms  The heart of this home is the stylishly updated kitchen, featuring Stainless Steel appliances, upgraded granite counters, plenty of cabinet and counter space.  Adjacent is the inviting dining area, perfect for gathering with family and friends.  The master bedroom exudes tranquility and boasts new update bathrooms. Additional bedrooms offer ample space and versatility, easily adaptable to your lifestyle.  Entertain or unwind on the deck, which offers picturesque views of the water, providing a serene backdrop for relaxation or outdoor gatherings.  Nestled in a sought-after area, this home offers not just comfort but also convenient access to community boardwalk, walking paths on the water. Embrace the lifestyle of water views coupled with the convenience of modern living.  Don't miss the chance to make this completely remodeled gem your own. Schedule a showing today and envision the possibilities this exceptional home holds.
